  <h2>How It Works</h2>
<div class="land_card col-sm-4">
<%= image_tag "pick_two.png", alt: "pick two students", width: 220 %>
<p>Speakit choose two students at random to talk in front of the class</p>
</div>
<div class="land_card col-sm-4">
<%= image_tag "talk_time.png", alt: "talk", width: 220 %>
<p>They start talking about the class topic and try to keep talking for 1-2 minutes</p>
</div>
<div class="land_card col-sm-4">
<%= image_tag "teacher_stop.png", alt: "teacher", width: 220 %>
<p>The teacher listens and stops students when they make a mistake, giving them 10 seconds to repair it</p>
</div>
<div class="col-sm-2"></div>
<div class="land_card col-sm-4">
<%= image_tag "idea.png", alt: "idea", width: 220 %>
<p>Students get chances to fix their mistakes but if they can't the conversation ends and another pair is chosen to speak</p>
</div>
<div class="land_card col-sm-4">
<%= image_tag "smartphone.png", alt: "smartphone", width: 220 %>
<p>Conversations are recorded using student's smartphones to review for homework</p>
